description:
The Gray Area Festival is four days of conference, performances, workshops, and exhibitions to gathers artists and philanthropists and discuss the impact of art and technology on culture. More at http://grayareafestival.io

Gray Area is non profit organization dedicated to applying art and technology to create positive social impact through education, civic engagement, and public programs.

We use digital tools to create art and design projects that benefit society. We test and scale projects with high impact potential, teach digital tools to support artists and technologists, and inspire our community by promoting meaningful new work.

More at http://grayarea.org
